{
  "texts": [
    "We termed these approaches as \"Similar\" and \"Random\" shot selection methods, respectively.",
    "In terms of quantity, (Fig. 3c, d) GPT-3.5 demonstrates significant superiority over the other models.",
    "It extracted the largest amount of data, comprising 4706 material-property value pairs using Random-shot and 4589 pairs using Similar-shot selection from the selected 6179 paragraphs.",
    "https://doi.org/10.1038/s43246-024-00708-9",
    "The NER-based MaterialsBERT pipeline extracted 3631 material-property pairs, slightly outperforming LLaMa, which extracted 3441 data pairs."
  ]
}